{"tid":789092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蝕錢！伊巴品牌A-Z玩完","createTime":"2018-08-22T03:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T04:09:21.000Z","uid":153600,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0fdc36906e3a369da44c2c8e3ee9bcfebd18a6","tid":789092,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=259ddd4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】瑞典鬼才伊巴謙莫域周身刀、張張利，究竟有沒有甚麼會難到他呢？<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯銀河射手伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）旗下服裝品牌A-Z因連續2年勁蝕，決定止蝕離場，退出時裝市場。挪威傳媒披露，意為Amateur to Zlatan的A-Z品牌，誕生兩年合共虧蝕2000萬歐元，前景暗淡，決定暫停生產。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴與挪威時裝品牌合作，因高昂的生產成本，導致入不敷支，並發表聯合聲明表示：「雖然去年錄得顯著增長，但這個歐洲新晉體育服裝品牌受到高昂成本所累，決定忍痛離開市場。」<br />\n<br />\n今年36歲的伊巴，曾效國際米蘭、巴塞隆拿、曼聯等勁旅，今年轉戰美職聯，曾代表瑞典國家隊116次的他，並未獲召用出戰今夏世界盃決賽周。"},{"pid":"2393b2be39e73065a2dcd81a65a1a6d2a98d508a","tid":789092,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"記得果陣開記招FAKE9晒班記者以為講轉會"},{"pid":"d141696bdecd476b789aeeccb4d52ee050540138","tid":789092,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SP&amp;message=6410408&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DSP%26message%3D6410408%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=78b2f3b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SP&amp;message=6410408&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n笑能死 震驚世界球壇記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人真係睇LIVE等佢講轉會 原來賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706a3e5534204f05c0cb26b7d6cd66305b641d3d","tid":789092,"uid":192158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f25246910410e8b53ed4bd363e4a5be8b5a2173c","tid":789092,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d4e1ae61743282acc5faacb93c7ae04e0b247d","tid":789092,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"兩年合共虧蝕2000萬歐元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1d4ba519c4f6a5269e3a6703e3be63d5beb85a","tid":789092,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:09:21.000Z","msg":"霸氣離場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}